subject: Volleyball
lead_paragraph: Phil Dalhausser and Todd Rogers won their second straight Manhattan Beach Open, beating eighth-seeded Sean Scott and Dax Holdren, 20-22, 21-16, 15-11. The third-seeded Dalhausser and Rogers had won just once in six previous A.V.P. Tour stops.
